        <mxCell id="Utq8LBualVHkBF1N58ms-0" value="[진행상태]&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;Head :&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 242, 204), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;미승인(01) -&amp;gt; 예정(11) -&amp;gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;재고부족(15) -&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 242, 204), rgb(255, 255, 255)); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;준비(17) -&amp;gt; 처리중(55) -&amp;gt; 확정(77) -&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;마감(91)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; -&amp;gt;강제확정(78) -&amp;gt; 취소(99)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;Detail :&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;미승인(01) -&amp;gt; 예정(11) -&amp;gt; 처리중(55) -&amp;gt; 확정(77) -&amp;gt; 취소(99)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;[수불유형]&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;출하 (OB)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;[상세유형]&amp;nbsp; 1.판매출하&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 242, 204), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(OB01) : &lt;b&gt;출하예정 -&amp;gt; 출하준비&amp;nbsp; -&amp;gt; 출고지시 -&amp;gt; 출고처리 -&amp;gt; 상차처리&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;2.마감후출하&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 242, 204), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(OB03):&lt;b&gt;출하예정 -&amp;gt; 출하준비&amp;nbsp; -&amp;gt; 출고지시 -&amp;gt; 출고처리 -&amp;gt; 상차처리&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;3.기타출하(OB05) :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;출하예정 -&amp;gt; 출하준비 -&amp;gt; 출고지시 -&amp;gt; 출고처리 -&amp;gt; 상차처리&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;4.외주직출(OB51) : &lt;b&gt;출하예정 -&amp;gt; 출하준비&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;-&amp;gt; 외주직출&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;5.센터출하(OB81) :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;출하예정 -&amp;gt; 출하준비&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;-&amp;gt; 출고지시 -&amp;gt; 출고처리 -&amp;gt; 상차처리&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;6.외주센터출하(OB83)&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 244, 195), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251);&quot;&gt;출하예정 -&amp;gt; 출하준비&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; -&amp;gt; 외주직출&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 242, 204), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;7.삭제오더(OB91) :&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;예정 -&amp;gt; 확정&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;8.외주직출(추가)(OB53)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 244, 195), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251);&quot;&gt;출하예정 -&amp;gt; 출하준비&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; -&amp;gt; 외주직출&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="strokeWidth=2;html=1;shape=mxgraph.flowchart.annotation_1;align=left;pointerEvents=1;shadow=0;" vertex="1" parent="AtAyEI1QQug8YpGFIPO_-1">
